{
  "_note": "Manifest for the label-only reverse-proxy shim stacks. Consumed by generate-proxy-stacks.py, which rewrites each compose/<name>/docker-compose.yml in place. Upstream host keys resolve against ../../../snippets/tailnet.json. Run the generator after editing; audit check 11-proxy-stacks gates drift.",
  "stacks": [
    {
      "name": "axon",
      "kind": "authelia-simple",
      "host": "axon",
      "upstream_var": "AXON_UPSTREAM",
      "upstream_host": "desktop",
      "upstream_port": 7070,
      "logging": false
    },
    {
      "name": "kl",
      "kind": "authelia-simple",
      "host": "kl",
      "upstream_var": "KL_UPSTREAM",
      "upstream_host": "desktop",
      "upstream_port": 6900,
      "logging": true
    },
    {
      "name": "music",
      "kind": "authelia-simple",
      "host": "music",
      "upstream_var": "MUSIC_UPSTREAM",
      "upstream_host": "desktop",
      "upstream_port": 8094,
      "logging": true
    },
    {
      "name": "vtag",
      "kind": "authelia-simple",
      "host": "vtag",
      "upstream_var": "VTAG_UPSTREAM",
      "upstream_host": "desktop",
      "upstream_port": 8093,
      "logging": true
    },
    {
      "name": "stt",
      "kind": "authelia-simple",
      "host": "stt",
      "upstream_var": "STT_UPSTREAM",
      "upstream_host": "desktop",
      "upstream_port": 8091,
      "request_body_max_size": "200MB",
      "logging": false
    },
    {
      "name": "semantic",
      "kind": "authelia-split",
      "host": "semantic",
      "comment": [
        "Reverse-proxy-only stack. semantic.mvr.ac is gated behind authelia and",
        "forwarded over tailscale to the visualizer running on mandragora-desktop",
        "({desktop}): the static frontend on :3001 and the FastAPI backend on",
        ":8000. /api/* is stripped and routed to the backend; everything else to",
        "the frontend. The backend runs LLM inference on the desktop GPU, so the",
        "authelia gate (two_factor) is mandatory — never expose this unauthenticated."
      ],
      "api_upstream_var": "SEMANTIC_API_UPSTREAM",
      "api_upstream_host": "desktop",
      "api_upstream_port": 8000,
      "web_upstream_var": "SEMANTIC_WEB_UPSTREAM",
      "web_upstream_host": "desktop",
      "web_upstream_port": 3001,
      "logging": false
    },
    {
      "name": "cv-es",
      "kind": "basic-auth",
      "host": "cv-es",
      "basic_auth_user": "edgard",
      "basic_auth_var": "CV_ES_BCRYPT",
      "upstream_var": "CV_ES_UPSTREAM",
      "upstream_host": "desktop",
      "upstream_port": 7691,
      "logging": false
    }
  ]
}
